<p><strong>Medium humanoid (elf), lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 18 (studded leather)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 135 (18d8+54)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 35 ft.</p>

